Qwen3-TTS for MLX-Swift
Copyright 2026 Xocialize

The Qwen3TTS and AudioCommon targets are derived from speech-swift
(https://github.com/soniqo/speech-swift, formerly ivan-digital/qwen3-asr-swift),
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Substantial modifications by Xocialize include: full-precision (bfloat16) weight
support alongside quantized weights (FlexibleLinear), symmetric trimming in
CausalTransposeConv1d, decode-length padding fixes, non-streaming text prefill,
tonal tail trimming, seed-once sampling fixes, a fresh SpeechTokenizerEncoder
implementation, and the Qwen3TTSCloning target (ICL voice cloning), which is
original work by Xocialize.

The Qwen3-TTS model weights are published separately by Alibaba/Qwen and the
mlx-community under the Apache License, Version 2.0; this repository contains
no model weights.
